# ============================================================
# NAME:    IQFeed / DTN
# TYPE:    Data Source (market data)
# REPO:    https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# UPDATED: 2026-07-08
# USED BY: NinjaTrader, SierraChart, ATAS (as a data feed)
# EXIT:    Route IQFeed to the SAME exit as the platform consuming it.
# NOTE:    LAN trading PCs proxy through Surge, so PROCESS-NAME does NOT apply to them; DOMAIN/IP rules route it.
# SOURCE:  Official IQFeed FAQ: login.interquote.com + 66.112.149.138-150 / 66.112.149.202-225 on ports 60000-60050.

DOMAIN,login.interquote.com
DOMAIN,iqhelp.dtn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,iqfeed.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,interquote.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dtn.com

# Official IQFeed FAQ lists:
# 66.112.149.138-150 and 66.112.149.202-225 on ports 60000-60050.
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.138/31,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.140/30,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.144/30,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.148/31,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.150/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.202/31,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.204/30,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.208/28,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.224/31,no-resolve
